description: Challenge endpoint referenced on the application homepage that returns 404 Not Found. The challenge link is visible on the main page but the endpoint is not implemented or deployed. Multiple path variations tested (xss-25, xss_25, /xss/25/, etc.) all return 404, suggesting the endpoint is intentionally disabled or has not been implemented.
notes: Despite being linked from the homepage, the /xss25 endpoint returns 404 Not Found for all HTTP methods. This suggests incomplete deployment or intentional disabling of challenge content. All path variations and case-sensitive versions also return 404, confirming the endpoint does not exist in the application's route configuration. Paths tested: /xss25, /XSS25, /xss-25, /xss_25, /xss/25, /xss25/, /challenge/xss25. HTTP methods tested: GET, HEAD, OPTIONS.
